<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/school_header') %>
    <main>
        <section class="academics-hero-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Our Academic Programs</h1>
                <p>Nurturing intelligence, fostering curiosity, and building a strong foundation for lifelong learning.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="curriculum-overview-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Comprehensive Curriculum for All-Round Growth</h2>
                <p>At N.R.K. Public School, we follow a well-structured curriculum designed to meet the academic standards set by the Central Board of Secondary Education (CBSE). Our approach goes beyond textbooks, focusing on practical understanding, critical thinking, and problem-solving skills.</p>
                <p>We provide education from Pre-Nursery to Class XII, ensuring a continuous and progressive learning journey. Our curriculum is tailored to cater to the diverse learning needs of students, preparing them for future academic challenges and real-world scenarios.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="teaching-methodology-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Innovative Teaching and Learning</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>**Experienced and Dedicated Faculty:** Our teachers are highly qualified, passionate, and continuously trained in modern pedagogical techniques to make learning engaging and effective.</li>
                    <li>**Interactive Classrooms:** We use interactive teaching aids, smart boards, and hands-on activities to encourage student participation and deeper understanding.</li>
                    <li>**Personalized Attention:** With a favorable student-teacher ratio, we ensure that each student receives individual attention, guidance, and support.</li>
                    <li>**Beyond Textbooks:** We integrate project-based learning, field trips, and workshops to provide practical exposure and connect classroom learning with real-life applications.</li>
                    <li>**Language Development:** Emphasis on English, Hindi, and local languages to foster effective communication skills.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="co-curricular-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Beyond Academics: Holistic Development</h2>
                <p>We believe in the holistic development of every child. Our co-curricular activities are an integral part of the learning process, helping students discover their talents and build essential life skills:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>**Sports and Physical Education:** Promoting health, teamwork, and discipline through various indoor and outdoor sports.</li>
                    <li>**Arts and Culture:** Encouraging creativity through music, dance, drama, and visual arts, celebrating India's rich cultural heritage.</li>
                    <li>**Clubs and Societies:** Offering opportunities for students to explore interests in science, literature, environment, and more.</li>
                    <li>**Community Service:** Instilling values of empathy and social responsibility through participation in community welfare programs.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="call-to-action">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Join Our Learning Community</h2>
                <p>Give your child the advantage of a comprehensive and empowering education.</p>
                <a href="/school/admissions" class="cta-button primary">View Admission Details</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>